ing: 1/2 (8 ounce) tub PHILADELPHIA Spicy Jalapeno Cream Cheese Spread
8 slices OSCAR MAYER Deli Fresh Smoked Turkey Breast
4 slices OSCAR MAYER Bacon, cooked, drained
1/2 red pepper, sliced into thin strips
des: "Spicy jalapeno cream cheese spread on tortillas is topped with turkey, bacon, avocado, and strips of red bell pepper in these quick snack or lunch wraps."
ins:
Spread tortillas with cream cheese.
Top with remaining ingredients; roll up.
